The architecture of AEM is built upon a modular design, which effectively segregates the presentation layer from both the content repository and the business logic 

4 foundational elements :
                             1. AEM
                        Application Layer
                           2. Apache Sling
                       Web Application Framework
                         3. Apache Jackrabbit Oak
                       JCR Repo / Storage Layer
                         4.  Apache Felix
                       OSGi Java Container



